config DYNAMENT_PLATINUM_HYDROCARBON
	bool "Dynament Platinum hydrocarbon gas sensor"
	default y
	depends on SENSOR
	depends on SERIAL
	depends on DT_HAS_ARGISENSE_DYNAMENT_PLATINUM_HYDROCARBON_ENABLED
	help
	  Enable the Dynament Platinum Series hydrocarbon infrared gas sensor
	  driver. The driver uses the live-data-simple UART protocol and exposes
	  methane concentration through ArgiSense private Sensor API channels.
